# Local secrets for `wrangler dev` / Cloudflare Worker runtime used by TanStack Start.
# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` and fill in the real value.
#
# Get the key from: Lovable → Project Settings → Cloud → Secrets
# (On the deployed Lovable preview/published site this is injected automatically —
#  .dev.vars is ONLY needed when running locally on your own machine.)
LOVABLE_API_KEY=your_lovable_api_key_here
